{"tid":2066360,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"解放軍殺左三名印度軍人","createTime":"2020-06-16T08:34:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-16T08:54:24.000Z","uid":210755,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"28bf6d58aadbef8110f190d468c3221096e34834","tid":2066360,"uid":210755,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:34:35.000Z","msg":"印度稱三名軍人在與中國軍隊衝突中死亡<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-53062219\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-53062219&d=St%2FdMm9ieZWtYGJEeV6aa9Dxg6radaiL0c7rOhjaEfM%3D&h=37e3351a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fzhongwen%2Ftrad%2Fworld-53062219&h=00857f5f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world-53062219</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n印度稱，三名印方士兵在與中國軍隊的衝突中死亡。中國外交部則發言要求印度不要單方面挑起事端。<br />\n據印度官方稱，三名印度士兵在拉德克爭議邊界與中國軍隊的衝突中死亡。印中雙方軍隊在這一爭議地區的對峙已經持續一段時間。<br />\n印度軍方表示，雙方高級別軍官正在會晤，以期緩和局勢。印方沒有做出進一步解釋。<br />\n<br />\n據信，這是印中雙方對峙以來第一次出現人員傷亡。"},{"pid":"461d2a43f765891486aa9ac9e250a76f2b0422ba","tid":2066360,"uid":24865,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-16T08:35:41.000Z","msg":"阿差你唔撚係忍佢老母啊 <img src=\"/assets/face